{"tid":688080,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"落艦有出路　C朗轉行打網球","createTime":"2018-06-02T23:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T02:20:07.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"73a1925f154b9aee3764ed353c3600fc4f16fbf2","tid":688080,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T23:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180602/photo/bkn-20180602215032698-0602_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180602215327\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180602%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180602215032698-0602_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180602215327&h=acf3da05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葡萄牙巨星C朗協助皇馬捧完歐聯冠軍之後，有得放假，可以延後向國家隊報到。不過，呢位射手並冇偷懶，休息之餘都要做下運動，但就係打網球，仲影相放上社交網。 <br />\n<br />\n見到C朗又騷哥利，影相時不忘展開手臂同大腿肌肉，完全係力嘅表現。從外型來睇計，仲健碩過唔少職業網球手。有傳C朗打算今夏離開「銀河艦隊」，但新球會又未有著落，莫非有意轉行打網球？"},{"pid":"31618da5135552283e221cef3a9eb124a0b214f7","tid":688080,"uid":61420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T23:51:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f63a338d4ea455ab77a58c4f291bb130b61bda4","tid":688080,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:18:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4eefb8e19485cfacab1ceeb62f20cae84bb20826","tid":688080,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"C朗 拿度"}]}